<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentc22cdfe4162a4878b9980ac3a6fec07c">
</div>
<p>The Westbourne Centre is a private, day hospital in the centre of the Edgbaston Medical Quarter in Birmingham.  We pride ourselves on intently listening and working <em>with </em>you, ensuring you receive the best care on your road to lasting health.  Our waiting times are proven to be some of the shortest in the country, we have no instances of MRSA contracted in hospital and excellent patient reviews.  Please choose <a href="http://www.westbournecentre.com/nhs-patients">The Westbourne Centre</a> for your next NHS procedure.</p>
<p> </p></div>
</div>
